Interface ScenarioFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

    • Method Detail

      • init

        void init(URL scenarioUrl)
   throws PerfCakeException
        Initializes all resources needed to prepare the scenario object. All I/O operations should happen here.
        Parameters:
        scenarioUrl - Location of the scenario file.
        Throws:
        PerfCakeException - When it was not possible to parse the scenario.

      • getScenario

        Scenario getScenario()
              throws PerfCakeException
        Constructs the scenario based on previously loaded data.
        Returns:
        Scenario instance specified in the file that has been loaded.
        Throws:
        PerfCakeException - When it was not possible to properly parese the loaded data.
